NOTE ON PHARMACEUTICAL USE

This software and its accompanying schema specification are provided under
the MIT license for the broadest possible adoption. They are intended to
support — not replace — a pharmaceutical company's existing Computer System
Validation (CSV) and Quality Management System (QMS) processes. Adopters are
responsible for validating any deployment of this software in a GxP
environment in accordance with applicable regulations (e.g., 21 CFR Part 11,
EU GMP Annex 11) and their own internal quality procedures.
